      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "By the decision of the Council of Ministers of the Government of Nepal dated 2071 Mangsir 16, the sub-metropolis was declared by merging 10 former VDCs, including Udaipur, Bhawaniapur, Piprahawa, Jaispur, Paraspur, Khaskarkando, Basudevpur, Manikapur, and Puraina."
